  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eTucked into a tree-lined area of East Hampton, New York, the \u003ca href=\"https://palettearch.com/project/shift-house/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShift House\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e is a new residential project by \u003ca href=\"https://palettearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePalette Architecture\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e that embodies a new paradigm in modern living, where design integrity meets the efficiencies of prefabricated construction. At just 1,600 square feet, this compact yet striking home is a compelling example of how modular building methods can coexist with high-end design and a deep connection to the natural world.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567949\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567949\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-2-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The rectangular swimming pool in the lush green backyard of Shift House is surrounded by trees, with a modern white building elegantly positioned on the left, creating a serene oasis.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-2-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn the wake of the COVID-19 pandemic, many New Yorkers found themselves reconsidering the environments they called home. The appeal of urban life – with its density, energy, and constant motion – gave way to a desire for peace, privacy, and proximity to nature. For one family of four, who already owned a townhouse in Brooklyn, the solution came in the form of a second home – one that would serve as a retreat, a workspace, and a space for togetherness in the calm of East Hampton’s wooded neighborhoods.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567950\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567950\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-3-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House is a modern single-story home with light wood siding, four windows, and a gravel driveway. It\u0026#39;s gracefully nestled amid lush greenery and trees, all under a clear blue sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-3-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis desire for a timely and affordable build led Palette Architecture to suggest an unconventional approach: modular prefabrication. With traditional construction plagued by material delays, workforce shortages, and rising costs, the firm saw an opportunity to sidestep these issues by turning to factory-fabricated modules. But this wasn’t simply a matter of expediency. The architects were determined to prove that modular design could be not just practical, but beautiful – and expressive of their clients’ values and lifestyles.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567951\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567951\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House is a modern single-story home featuring a sleek wooden exterior, flat roof, and expansive windows. A gravel driveway leads to the neatly landscaped garden with lush grass and shrubs, all nestled amid towering trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-4-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eModular construction often carries a reputation for compromise: cramped layouts, uninspired aesthetics, and limited flexibility. Palette Architecture sought to break these assumptions from the start. The design of Shift House was driven by both the possibilities and the constraints of prefabrication. With transportation size restrictions dictating module dimensions, the team had to think creatively about spatial composition.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567952\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567952\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Shift House is a modern flat-roofed home featuring elegant wood paneling, a covered wooden porch, and a beautifully landscaped garden. A stone path meanders through the greenery, while the gravel driveway adds to its serene charm.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-5-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe final configuration is deceptively simple: three main modules form the structural core of the home – housing bedrooms, bathrooms, and a generous open-plan living area. To add volume and light to the central gathering space, five prefabricated panels were designed to lift the ceiling height well beyond standard modular limits. This move not only enhanced the interior experience but also demonstrated how strategic interventions can elevate prefab architecture into something truly special.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567953\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567953\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern wooden Shift House exterior with a small porch complements the yard\u0026#39;s green grass and stepping stones leading to the entrance. Trees and a rustic wooden fence create a serene backdrop.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe modules were manufactured offsite with remarkable precision, arriving ready for rapid assembly. In fact, the entire structure was erected in a single day, complete with mechanical, electrical, and plumbing systems in place. Afterward, onsite crews completed the finishes, cladding, and select millwork – blending factory efficiency with handcrafted detail.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567954\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567954\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m-810x1090.jpg\" alt=\"Sunlight illuminates Shift House, casting intricate shadows of vertical wooden slats onto the tiled floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1090\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m-810x1090.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m-800x1077.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m-768x1034.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m-1141x1536.jpg 1141w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-6m.jpg 128