pg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-9-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567958\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567958\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room in the Shift House features a large black cabinet with a built-in bookshelf filled with colorful books. Large windows reveal a stunning view of greenery outside, while a light gray couch is partially visible.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLarge windows dominate the living and dining areas, turning the interior into a frame for the outdoors. Whether cooking in the kitchen, relaxing with family, or waking up in one of the bedrooms, views of the verdant surroundings are always close at hand.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567959\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567959\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House offers a spacious dining area with a wooden table, light green chairs, a large round ceiling lamp, and expansive windows revealing a stunning view of the garden and pool.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567960\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567960\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-12-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House kitchen boasts modern elegance with white cabinets and a marble island paired with wooden stools. Large windows illuminate the light wood flooring and gray tiled backsplash. A sliding glass door opens to a deck, inviting you to enjoy the greenery outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-12-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-12-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe house departs from the sterility sometimes associated with modular construction. Instead, it’s warm, textural, and carefully curated. Custom millwork is used not only to add to the aesthetics but also to help visually tie the modular components together. Each room is given a distinct material identity – through cabinet finishes, wood tones, and subtle design cues – creating a sense of discovery and depth within a relatively modest footprint.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567961\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567961\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House features a modern kitchen with white cabinets, a marble countertop, and a light wood floor. Large windows flood the space with natural light, while a gray rug adds warmth. Green trees frame the view outside, seamlessly blending nature with contemporary design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567962\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567962\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-14-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House features a modern kitchen and dining area with large windows, crisp white cabinets, an inviting island, and a wooden table. Glass doors seamlessly open to reveal the lush green garden beyond.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-14-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-14-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567963\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567963\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-15-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House-inspired bedroom features a modern aesthetic with a large bed, light wood flooring, and a built-in wardrobe. Natural light floods in through two windows, while a cozy rug is placed beside the bed for added comfort.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-15-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-15-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe natural materials selected for the interiors further echo the surrounding landscape. Wood grains, organic textures, and earthy tones are paired with minimalist forms to create a modern yet inviting atmosphere. This balance between simplicity and character is a hallmark of Palette Architecture’s approach.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567964\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567964\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House features a modern bathroom complete with a double sink vanity, elegant wood cabinets, and irregular mirrors. Tiled walls complement the glass-enclosed shower, while ample natural light pours through a rectangular window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-16-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567965\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567965\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"The modern bathroom at Shift House features blue tiled walls, a terrazzo floor, and a sleek bathtub. Black fixtures complement the elegant design, while a light above the mirror and a skylight on the ceiling enhance the airy atmosphere.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567966\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567966\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18-810x1082.jpg\" alt=\"A modern shower in Shift House features glass doors, a rainfall showerhead, and elegantly greenish-gray tiled walls.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1082\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18-810x1082.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18-800x1069.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18-768x1026.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18-1150x1536.jpg 1150w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567967\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567967\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-19-810x513.jpg\" alt=\"Diagram illustrating five design concepts (A-E) for modular spaces, including the innovative Shift House model. Each concept features stages showing shipping, family space, and overlapped module in various configurations.\" width=\"810\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-19-810x513.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-19-800x507.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-19-768x487.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567968\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567968\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-20-810x407.jpg\" alt=\"Illustration of an exploded architectural view of a Shift House, showcasing its modular building sections arranged in a linear and vertical layout.\" width=\"810\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-20-810x407.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-20-800x402.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-20-768x386.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567969\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567969\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-21-810x566.jpg\" alt=\"The Shift House floor plan showcases a single-story layout with two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and inviting living and dining areas. It features a modern kitchen and a garage for one car. Steps gracefully lead to an outdoor space surrounded by trees, blending nature with comfort.\" width=\"810\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-21-810x566.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-21-800x559.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-21-768x536.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/Shift-House-East-Hamptom-New-York-Palette-Architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on Palette Architecture or Shift House, visit \u003ca href=\"https://palettearch.com/project/shift-house/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003epalettearch.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.jodykivort.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eJody Kivort\u003c/a\u003e, courtesy of \u003ca href=\"https://www.v2com-newswire.com/en/newsroom/press-kits/a2e2e86eb8301fbcbc9d54eb262fac829c359cae646bb9a99dd48d7e1144f3fca1859ad1da0302ef3a393c3649cb07b09aa09b9ddd1e52fba7a9ed4ac48e84d4/shift-house-e8ffca3e-cd08-4cff-8346-245e46e70001\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer\"\u003ev2com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
